---
title: Za'atar-Crusted Beef Tenderloin with Roasted Veggies, Pistachio Couscous & Creamy Lemon Sauce
description: True to its name, beef tenderloin is luxuriously tender. Here, it’s dusted in herbal, tart, and peppery za'atar spice, then is seared to a deep brown, and drizzled with a rich lemony cream sauce. A bed of pistachio and apricot-studded pearl couscous is ideal for catching extra sauce, while sumac roasted vegetables make a deliciously caramelized side.
